title: erroneous null JSON-RPC result for eth_getTransactionReceipt for one particular transaction hash

body: +1 on this. We have a custom EVM chain and get null receipts for large ranges of blocks. Updated to latest 1.21, turned up log levels to TRACE, tried the FixReceipts option, deleted the db and did a resync, nothing works. Except parity_getBlockReceipts will fetch the receipt just fine, so it is there.

+1 on this as well. We are observing this intermittently with our instances of Gnosis chain - Fortunately FixReceipts does fix it for us, however it's a 2.5hr downtime each time the node hits this issue.
